STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Daron WILKINSON, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-2006 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A defendant challenges the sentence imposed on his conviction for theft in the second degree. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
